('The Lord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring', 'Young hobbit Frodo Baggins, after inheriting a mysterious ring from his uncle Bilbo, must leave his home in order to keep it from falling into the hands of its evil creator. Along the way, a fellowship is formed to protect the ringbearer and make sure that the ring arrives at its final destination: Mt. Doom, the only place where it can be destroyed.', 2001, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6oom5QYQ2yQTMJIbnvbkBL9cHo6.jpg', NULL, NULL, 'en', 1),
